{
    "title": "How to learn Javascript",
    "content": "<h1 data-start=\"106\" data-end=\"171\">\uD83D\uDE80 JavaScript for Beginners: The Ultimate Getting Started Guide<\/h1>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"173\" data-end=\"414\">JavaScript is one of the most powerful and widely used programming languages on the web. Whether you're building interactive websites, server-side applications, or browser extensions, JavaScript is a must-know tool in your developer toolbox.<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"173\" data-end=\"414\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"173\" data-end=\"414\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<hr data-start=\"416\" data-end=\"419\">\r\n<h2 data-start=\"421\" data-end=\"446\">\uD83D\uDCCC What is JavaScript?<\/h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"448\" data-end=\"657\">JavaScript is a scripting language that runs in the browser and enables interactive web pages. It was created in 1995 by Brendan Eich and has since become a core part of web development alongside HTML and CSS.<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"659\" data-end=\"776\">Today, JavaScript also runs on servers (thanks to Node.js) and powers modern frameworks like React, Vue, and Angular.<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"659\" data-end=\"776\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"659\" data-end=\"776\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<hr data-start=\"778\" data-end=\"781\">\r\n<h2 data-start=\"783\" data-end=\"810\">\uD83D\uDCCB Why Learn JavaScript?<\/h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"812\" data-end=\"1094\">\r\n    <li data-start=\"812\" data-end=\"858\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"814\" data-end=\"858\">\u2705 It\u2019s everywhere \u2013 all browsers support it.<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"859\" data-end=\"944\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"861\" data-end=\"944\">\u2705 Highly in demand \u2013 essential for front-end, back-end, and full-stack development.<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"945\" data-end=\"1014\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"947\" data-end=\"1014\">\u2705 Huge ecosystem \u2013 vast number of tools, libraries, and frameworks.<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"1015\" data-end=\"1094\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"1017\" data-end=\"1094\">\u2705 Beginner-friendly \u2013 easy to start with and experiment live in your browser.<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"1017\" data-end=\"1094\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1017\" data-end=\"1094\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<hr data-start=\"1096\" data-end=\"1099\">\r\n<h2 data-start=\"1101\" data-end=\"1128\">\uD83E\uDDF0 Setting Up JavaScript<\/h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1130\" data-end=\"1228\">You don't need anything fancy to get started. Just open your browser and use the DevTools console:<\/p>\r\n<ol data-start=\"1230\" data-end=\"1365\">\r\n    <li data-start=\"1230\" data-end=\"1261\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"1233\" data-end=\"1261\">Open Chrome (or any browser)<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"1262\" data-end=\"1298\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"1265\" data-end=\"1298\">Press <code data-start=\"1271\" data-end=\"1276\">F12<\/code> or <code data-start=\"1280\" data-end=\"1298\">Ctrl + Shift + I<\/code><\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"1299\" data-end=\"1325\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"1302\" data-end=\"1325\">Go to the \u201CConsole\u201D tab<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"1326\" data-end=\"1365\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"1329\" data-end=\"1365\">Type: <code data-start=\"1335\" data-end=\"1365\">console.log('Hello, World!')<\/code><\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n<\/ol>\r\n<p data-start=\"1367\" data-end=\"1425\">You\u2019ve just written and run your first JavaScript program!<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1367\" data-end=\"1425\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1367\" data-end=\"1425\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<hr data-start=\"1427\" data-end=\"1430\">\r\n<h2 data-start=\"1432\" data-end=\"1465\">\uD83E\uDDE0 Core Concepts You Must Know<\/h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"1467\" data-end=\"1498\">1. Variables and Data Types<\/h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1499\" data-end=\"1562\">JavaScript uses <code data-start=\"1515\" data-end=\"1520\">let<\/code>, <code data-start=\"1522\" data-end=\"1529\">const<\/code>, and <code data-start=\"1535\" data-end=\"1540\">var<\/code> to declare variables.<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1564\" data-end=\"1572\">Example:<\/p>\r\n<div class=\"contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary\">\r\n    <div class=\"flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]\">js<\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"whitespace-pre! language-js\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let<\/span><span> name = <\/span><span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Alice\"<\/span><span>;\r\n            <\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const<\/span><span> age = <\/span><span class=\"hljs-number\">25<\/span><span>;\r\n            <\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">var<\/span><span> isStudent = <\/span><span class=\"hljs-literal\">true<\/span><span>;\r\n            <\/span><\/code><\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<p data-start=\"1642\" data-end=\"1661\">Data types include:<\/p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1662\" data-end=\"1730\">\r\n    <li data-start=\"1662\" data-end=\"1671\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"1664\" data-end=\"1671\">Strings<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"1672\" data-end=\"1681\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"1674\" data-end=\"1681\">Numbers<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"1682\" data-end=\"1692\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"1684\" data-end=\"1692\">Booleans<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"1693\" data-end=\"1701\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"1695\" data-end=\"1701\">Arrays<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"1702\" data-end=\"1711\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"1704\" data-end=\"1711\">Objects<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"1712\" data-end=\"1730\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"1714\" data-end=\"1730\">Null \/ Undefined<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"1714\" data-end=\"1730\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1714\" data-end=\"1730\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<hr data-start=\"1732\" data-end=\"1735\">\r\n<h3 data-start=\"1737\" data-end=\"1753\">2. Functions<\/h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1754\" data-end=\"1792\">Functions are reusable blocks of code.<\/p>\r\n<div class=\"contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary\">\r\n    <div class=\"flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]\">js<\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"sticky top-9\">\r\n        <div class=\"absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2\">\r\n            <div class=\"bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary text-token-text-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary flex items-center rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs\">&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"whitespace-pre! language-js\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-title function_\">greet<\/span><span>(<\/span><span class=\"hljs-params\">name<\/span><span>) {\r\n                &nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Hello, \"<\/span><span> + name + <\/span><span class=\"hljs-string\">\"!\"<\/span><span>;\r\n                }<\/span><\/code><\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"whitespace-pre! language-js\"><span>\r\n            <\/span><\/code><\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<hr data-start=\"1863\" data-end=\"1866\">\r\n<h3 data-start=\"1868\" data-end=\"1887\">3. Conditionals<\/h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1888\" data-end=\"1935\">Use <code data-start=\"1892\" data-end=\"1896\">if<\/code>, <code data-start=\"1898\" data-end=\"1904\">else<\/code>, and <code data-start=\"1910\" data-end=\"1918\">switch<\/code> to control flow:<\/p>\r\n<div class=\"contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary\">\r\n    <div class=\"flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]\">js<\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"sticky top-9\">\r\n        <div class=\"absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2\">\r\n            <div class=\"bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary text-token-text-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary flex items-center rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs\">&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"whitespace-pre! language-js\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if<\/span><span> (age &gt; <\/span><span class=\"hljs-number\">18<\/span><span>) {\r\n                &nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console<\/span><span>.<\/span><span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log<\/span><span>(<\/span><span class=\"hljs-string\">\"You are an adult.\"<\/span><span>);\r\n                } <\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else<\/span><span> {\r\n                &nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console<\/span><span>.<\/span><span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log<\/span><span>(<\/span><span class=\"hljs-string\">\"You are a minor.\"<\/span><span>);\r\n                }<\/span><\/code><\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"whitespace-pre! language-js\"><span>\r\n            <\/span><\/code><\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<hr data-start=\"2046\" data-end=\"2049\">\r\n<h3 data-start=\"2051\" data-end=\"2063\">4. Loops<\/h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"2064\" data-end=\"2095\">Run repeated logic using loops:<\/p>\r\n<div class=\"contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary\">\r\n    <div class=\"flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]\">js<\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"sticky top-9\">\r\n        <div class=\"absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2\">\r\n            <div class=\"bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary text-token-text-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary flex items-center rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs\">&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"whitespace-pre! language-js\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for<\/span><span> (<\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let<\/span><span> i = <\/span><span class=\"hljs-number\">0<\/span><span>; i &lt; <\/span><span class=\"hljs-number\">5<\/span><span>; i++) {\r\n                &nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console<\/span><span>.<\/span><span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log<\/span><span>(i);\r\n                }<\/span><\/code><\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"whitespace-pre! language-js\"><span>\r\n            <\/span><\/code><\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<hr data-start=\"2158\" data-end=\"2161\">\r\n<h2 data-start=\"2163\" data-end=\"2194\">\uD83C\uDF10 JavaScript in the Browser<\/h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"2196\" data-end=\"2258\">You can add JavaScript directly to HTML using <code data-start=\"2242\" data-end=\"2252\">&lt;script&gt;<\/code> tags.<\/p>\r\n<div class=\"contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary\">\r\n    <div class=\"flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]\">html<\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"sticky top-9\">\r\n        <div class=\"absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2\">\r\n            <div class=\"bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary text-token-text-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary flex items-center rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs\">&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"whitespace-pre! language-html\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<\/span><span class=\"hljs-tag hljs-name\">script<\/span><span>&gt;<\/span><span class=\"language-javascript\">\r\n                &nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert<\/span><span>(<\/span><span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Welcome to my site!\"<\/span><span>);\r\n            <\/span><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;\/<\/span><span class=\"hljs-tag hljs-name\">script<\/span><span>&gt;\r\n            <\/span><\/code><\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<p data-start=\"2324\" data-end=\"2380\">You can also manipulate HTML elements using the DOM API.<\/p>\r\n<div class=\"contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary\">\r\n    <div class=\"flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]\">js<\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"sticky top-9\">\r\n        <div class=\"absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2\">\r\n            <div class=\"bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary text-token-text-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary flex items-center rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs\">&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"whitespace-pre! language-js\"><span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">document<\/span><span>.<\/span><span class=\"hljs-title function_\">getElementById<\/span><span>(<\/span><span class=\"hljs-string\">\"demo\"<\/span><span>).<\/span><span class=\"hljs-property\">innerText<\/span><span> = <\/span><span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Changed!\"<\/span><span>;<\/span><\/code><\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"whitespace-pre! language-js\"><span>\r\n            <\/span><\/code><\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<hr data-start=\"2449\" data-end=\"2452\">\r\n<h2 data-start=\"2454\" data-end=\"2483\">\uD83D\uDD04 Asynchronous JavaScript<\/h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"2485\" data-end=\"2568\">JavaScript supports asynchronous code using callbacks, promises, and <code data-start=\"2554\" data-end=\"2567\">async\/await<\/code>.<\/p>\r\n<div class=\"contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary\">\r\n    <div class=\"flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]\">js<\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"sticky top-9\">\r\n        <div class=\"absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2\">\r\n            <div class=\"bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary text-token-text-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary flex items-center rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs\">&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"whitespace-pre! language-js\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">async<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-title function_\">fetchData<\/span><span>(<\/span><span class=\"hljs-params\"><\/span><span>) {\r\n                &nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let<\/span><span> response = <\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">await<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-title function_\">fetch<\/span><span>(<\/span><span class=\"hljs-string\">\"https:\/\/api.example.com\/data\"<\/span><span>);\r\n                &nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let<\/span><span> data = <\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">await<\/span><span> response.<\/span><span class=\"hljs-title function_\">json<\/span><span>();\r\n                &nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">console<\/span><span>.<\/span><span class=\"hljs-title function_\">log<\/span><span>(data);\r\n                }<\/span><\/code><\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"whitespace-pre! language-js\"><span>\r\n            <\/span><\/code><\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<hr data-start=\"2731\" data-end=\"2734\">\r\n<h2 data-start=\"2736\" data-end=\"2771\">\uD83D\uDCE6 Popular JavaScript Frameworks<\/h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"2773\" data-end=\"2938\">\r\n    <li data-start=\"2773\" data-end=\"2802\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"2775\" data-end=\"2802\"><strong data-start=\"2775\" data-end=\"2784\">React<\/strong> \u2013 for building UI<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"2803\" data-end=\"2848\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"2805\" data-end=\"2848\"><strong data-start=\"2805\" data-end=\"2812\">Vue<\/strong> \u2013 lightweight and beginner-friendly<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"2849\" data-end=\"2898\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"2851\" data-end=\"2898\"><strong data-start=\"2851\" data-end=\"2862\">Angular<\/strong> \u2013 full-featured for enterprise apps<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"2899\" data-end=\"2938\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"2901\" data-end=\"2938\"><strong data-start=\"2901\" data-end=\"2912\">Node.js<\/strong> \u2013 for backend development<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"2901\" data-end=\"2938\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"2901\" data-end=\"2938\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<hr data-start=\"2940\" data-end=\"2943\">\r\n<h2 data-start=\"2945\" data-end=\"2969\">\uD83D\uDEE0 Tips for Beginners<\/h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"2971\" data-end=\"3201\">\r\n    <li data-start=\"2971\" data-end=\"3023\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"2973\" data-end=\"3023\">Practice small projects (to-do lists, calculators)<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"3024\" data-end=\"3060\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"3026\" data-end=\"3060\">Read documentation (MDN is great!)<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"3061\" data-end=\"3102\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"3063\" data-end=\"3102\">Avoid jumping into frameworks too early<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"3103\" data-end=\"3172\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"3105\" data-end=\"3172\">Learn the basics first: DOM, events, arrays, objects, and functions<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"3173\" data-end=\"3201\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"3175\" data-end=\"3201\">Build, break, fix, repeat!<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"3175\" data-end=\"3201\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"3175\" data-end=\"3201\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<hr data-start=\"3203\" data-end=\"3206\">\r\n<h2 data-start=\"3208\" data-end=\"3224\">\uD83C\uDFC1 Conclusion<\/h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"3226\" data-end=\"3392\">JavaScript is a fun and incredibly valuable language. Once you get the hang of the basics, the possibilities are endless\u2014from interactive websites to entire web apps.<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"3394\" data-end=\"3460\">Start writing code today and explore the world of web development!<\/p>",
